::Blue Reeker::


Blue Reeker looks around the Alliance base. She yawns, after all it was a 
long day. She starts to head for her room. She then slaps herself in the 
head. She doesn't have a room. she heads for the bridge to ask Zardus where 
her room is. She walked into the bridge, no Zardus. She goes outside and 
sees Zardus with a bunch of guys. She walks up to Zardus "Where is my room, 
commander" sh then looks at Hell beast and gives a wink.
